{"prompt": "Design a dynamic e-commerce store for a custom apparel brand. The aesthetic should incorporate a bold fuchsia.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Custom Threads</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #f0f0f0;\n            color: #333;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n        header {\n            background-color: #e6007e;\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding-top: 30px;\n            min-height: 70px;\n            border-bottom: #c20069 3px solid;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0 0 10px 0;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n        }\n        nav {\n            background-color: #c20069;\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 10px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n        nav a {\n            color: #ffffff;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            padding: 5px 15px;\n            margin: 0 5px;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        nav a:hover {\n            background-color: #e6007e;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n        }\n        #hero {\n            background: linear-gradient(rgba(230, 0, 126, 0.7), rgba(230, 0, 126, 0.7)), url('https://via.placeholder.com/1500x500/e6007e/ffffff?text=Your+Custom+Apparel') no-repeat center center/cover;\n            height: 500px;\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            text-align: center;\n            color: #ffffff;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n        #hero h2 {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n        #hero p {\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n        .btn {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: #ffffff;\n            color: #e6007e;\n            padding: 12px 30px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .btn:hover {\n            background-color: #f0f0f0;\n            color: #c20069;\n        }\n        .product-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));\n            gap: 20px;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n        .product {\n            background-color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 20px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n            text-align: center;\n            border: 1px solid #e6007e;\n        }\n        .product img {\n            max-width: 100%;\n            height: 200px;\n            object-fit: cover;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n        }\n        .product h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            color: #e6007e;\n        }\n        .product .price {\n            font-weight: bold;\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            color: #e6007e;\n        }\n        .product .btn-buy {\n            background-color: #e6007e;\n            color: #ffffff;\n            margin-top: 15px;\n        }\n        .product .btn-buy:hover {\n            background-color: #c20069;\n        }\n        footer {\n            background-color: #333;\n            color: #ffffff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n        }\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n        /* Form Styling */\n        .customization-form {\n            background-color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n            margin-top: 20px;\n            border: 1px solid #e6007e;\n        }\n        .customization-form h3 {\n            color: #e6007e;\n            margin-top: 0;\n        }\n        .form-group {\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n        }\n        .form-group label {\n            display: block;\n            margin-bottom: 5px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n        }\n        .form-group input[type=\"text\"],\n        .form-group input[type=\"email\"],\n        .form-group textarea,\n        .form-group select {\n            width: 100%;\n            padding: 10px;\n            border: 1px solid #ccc;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            box-sizing: border-box; /* Important for consistent sizing */\n        }\n        .form-group textarea {\n            min-height: 100px;\n            resize: vertical;\n        }\n        .form-group .color-picker {\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n        }\n        .form-group .color-picker input[type=\"color\"] {\n            width: 50px;\n            height: 30px;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            margin-left: 10px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n        }\n        .form-group button {\n            background-color: #e6007e;\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 12px 30px;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n            width: auto;\n        }\n        .form-group button:hover {\n            background-color: #c20069;\n        }\n        .product-detail-section {\n            background-color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n            margin-top: 20px;\n            border: 1px solid #e6007e;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-wrap: wrap;\n            gap: 30px;\n        }\n        .product-detail-section .product-image {\n            flex: 1 1 300px;\n        }\n        .product-detail-section .product-image img {\n            max-width: 100%;\n            height: auto;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n        }\n        .product-detail-section .product-info {\n            flex: 2 1 400px;\n        }\n        .product-info h2 {\n            color: #e6007e;\n            margin-top: 0;\n        }\n        .product-info .price {\n            font-size: 1.8em;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            color: #e6007e;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n        .product-info p {\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n        }\n        .add-to-cart-form {\n            margin-top: 25px;\n            padding: 20px;\n            background-color: #f8f8f8;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n        }\n        .add-to-cart-form label {\n            font-weight: bold;\n            margin-right: 10px;\n        }\n        .add-to-cart-form select,\n        .add-to-cart-form input[type=\"number\"] {\n            padding: 8px;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            border: 1px solid #ccc;\n            margin-right: 10px;\n        }\n        .add-to-cart-form button {\n            background-color: #e6007e;\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 10px 20px;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .add-to-cart-form button:hover {\n            background-color: #c20069;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>Custom Threads</h1>\n            <p>Your Vision, Our Apparel.</p>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n    <nav>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <a href=\"#home\">Home</a>\n            <a href=\"#products\">Products</a>\n            <a href=\"#customize\">Customize</a>\n            <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n        </div>\n    </nav>\n\n    <section id=\"hero\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Design Your Dream Apparel</h2>\n            <p>High-quality custom t-shirts, hoodies, and more. Unleash your creativity!</p>\n            <a href=\"#customize\" class=\"btn\">Start Designing</a>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <section id=\"products\">\n            <h2>Featured Products</h2>\n            <div class=\"product-grid\">\n                <div class=\"product\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x250/e6007e/ffffff?text=T-Shirt\" alt=\"Custom T-Shirt\">\n                    <h3>Premium Cotton Tee</h3>\n                    <p>Soft, durable, and perfect for any design.</p>\n                    <p class=\"price\">$24.99</p>\n                    <a href=\"#product-1\" class=\"btn btn-buy\">View Details</a>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"product\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x250/e6007e/ffffff?text=Hoodie\" alt=\"Custom Hoodie\">\n                    <h3>Cozy Fleece Hoodie</h3>\n                    <p>Stay warm and stylish with our premium fleece.</p>\n                    <p class=\"price\">$49.99</p>\n                    <a href=\"#product-2\" class=\"btn btn-buy\">View Details</a>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"product\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x250/e6007e/ffffff?text=Sweatshirt\" alt=\"Custom Sweatshirt\">\n                    <h3>Classic Crewneck Sweatshirt</h3>\n                    <p>A timeless classic for everyday comfort.</p>\n                    <p class=\"price\">$39.99</p>\n                    <a href=\"#product-3\" class=\"btn btn-buy\">View Details</a>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"customize\" class=\"customization-form\">\n            <h3>Create Your Own Masterpiece</h3>\n            <form id=\"customizationForm\">\n                <div class=\"form-group\">\n                    <label for=\"productType\">Product Type:</label>\n                    <select id=\"productType\" name=\"productType\">\n                        <option value=\"tshirt\">T-Shirt</option>\n                        <option value=\"hoodie\">Hoodie</option>\n                        <option value=\"sweatshirt\">Sweatshirt</option>\n                    </select>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"form-group\">\n                    <label for=\"baseColor\">Base Color:</label>\n                    <div class=\"color-picker\">\n                        <input type=\"color\" id=\"baseColor\" name=\"baseColor\" value=\"#ffffff\">\n                        <span>(Choose your garment's base color)</span>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"form-group\">\n                    <label for=\"designText\">Design Text (Optional):</label>\n                    <input type=\"text\" id=\"designText\" name=\"designText\" placeholder=\"e.g., Your Brand Name\">\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"form-group\">\n                    <label for=\"uploadDesign\">Upload Your Design (Optional):</label>\n                    <input type=\"file\" id=\"uploadDesign\" name=\"uploadDesign\" accept=\"image/*\">\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"form-group\">\n                    <label for=\"specialInstructions\">Special Instructions:</label>\n                    <textarea id=\"specialInstructions\" name=\"specialInstructions\" placeholder=\"Any specific placement, font requests, etc.\"></textarea>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"form-group\">\n                    <button type=\"submit\">Add to Cart & Customize</button>\n                </div>\n            </form>\n        </section>\n\n        <!-- Example Product Detail Page (could be dynamic) -->\n        <section id=\"product-1\" class=\"product-detail-section\" style=\"display: none;\">\n            <div class=\"product-image\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/500x500/e6007e/ffffff?text=Premium+T-Shirt\" alt=\"Premium Cotton Tee\">\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"product-info\">\n                <h2>Premium Cotton Tee</h2>\n                <p class=\"price\">$24.99</p>\n                <p>Experience ultimate comfort with our 100% premium cotton t-shirt. Available in a wide range of vibrant colors, this tee is perfect for everyday wear or as a canvas for your custom designs. Features a relaxed fit and durable stitching.</p>\n                <div class=\"add-to-cart-form\">\n                    <label for=\"quantity\">Qty:</label>\n                    <input type=\"number\" id=\"quantity\" name=\"quantity\" value=\"1\" min=\"1\">\n                    <label for=\"size\">Size:</label>\n                    <select id=\"size\" name=\"size\">\n                        <option value=\"s\">S</option>\n                        <option value=\"m\">M</option>\n                        <option value=\"l\">L</option>\n                        <option value=\"xl\">XL</option>\n                    </select>\n                    <button type=\"button\" onclick=\"addToCart('Premium Cotton Tee', 24.99)\">Add to Cart</button>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n         <section id=\"product-2\" class=\"product-detail-section\" style=\"display: none;\">\n            <div class=\"product-image\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/500x500/e6007e/ffffff?text=Cozy+Hoodie\" alt=\"Cozy Fleece Hoodie\">\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"product-info\">\n                <h2>Cozy Fleece Hoodie</h2>\n                <p class=\"price\">$49.99</p>\n                <p>Wrap yourself in warmth with our ultra-soft fleece hoodie. Designed for maximum comfort and style, it features a double-lined hood, front pouch pocket, and is perfect for those cooler days or for showcasing your unique designs. Available in multiple colors.</p>\n                 <div class=\"add-to-cart-form\">\n                    <label for=\"quantity\">Qty:</label>\n                    <input type=\"number\" id=\"quantity\" name=\"quantity\" value=\"1\" min=\"1\">\n                    <label for=\"size\">Size:</label>\n                    <select id=\"size\" name=\"size\">\n                        <option value=\"s\">S</option>\n                        <option value=\"m\">M</option>\n                        <option value=\"l\">L</option>\n                        <option value=\"xl\">XL</option>\n                    </select>\n                    <button type=\"button\" onclick=\"addToCart('Cozy Fleece Hoodie', 49.99)\">Add to Cart</button>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n         <section id=\"product-3\" class=\"product-detail-section\" style=\"display: none;\">\n            <div class=\"product-image\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/500x500/e6007e/ffffff?text=Crewneck+Sweatshirt\" alt=\"Classic Crewneck Sweatshirt\">\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"product-info\">\n                <h2>Classic Crewneck Sweatshirt</h2>\n                <p class=\"price\">$39.99</p>\n                <p>A versatile essential, our classic crewneck sweatshirt offers a comfortable fit and timeless appeal. Made from a soft, durable blend, it's ideal for layering or wearing on its own. Perfect for casual outings and personalized with your custom artwork.</p>\n                 <div class=\"add-to-cart-form\">\n                    <label for=\"quantity\">Qty:</label>\n                    <input type=\"number\" id=\"quantity\" name=\"quantity\" value=\"1\" min=\"1\">\n                    